Paper: hep-th/9807119

Date: 1998-07-17

Title: Master Equations for Master Amplitudes

Authors: M. Caffo, H. Czyz, S. Laporta and E. Remiddi

Comments: 11 pages, Latex, 1 encapsulated Postscript figure with epsfig, some

references added; Talk presented at the Zeuthen Workshop on ElementaryParticle Physics - Loops and Legs in Gauge Theories - Rheinsberg, 19-24 April1998Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B29 (1998) 2627-2635

The general lines of the derivation and the main properties of the masterequations for the master amplitudes associated to a given Feynman graph arerecalled. Some results for the 2-loop self-mass graph with 4 propagators arethen presented.